~~ Compilation ~~
run `cmake` and build with chosen build tools

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Some code in this project were originally made as a project for course work at the University of Waterloo.

Under University of Waterloo Policy 73 IP for work created in the course of learning (Scholarly Work) is owned by the creator
(https://uwaterloo.ca/secretariat/policies-procedures-guidelines/policies/policy-73-intellectual-property-rights)

original source can be found at private repo on university server (request for permission required for access):
https://git.uwaterloo.ca/wdbrown/cs488-assignments

