Refractive materials and soft-reflection implemented partially using reference:
"Raytracing in a Weekend", Peter Shirley, 2018
retrieved from: https://www.realtimerendering.com/raytracing/Ray%20Tracing%20in%20a%20Weekend.pdf
original source License found at: 
https://github.com/RayTracing/InOneWeekend/blob/master/COPYING.txt

